    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Validation evidence demonstrates R² = 0.94 and Pearson r = 0.97 on the hemolysis model calibration dataset, with RMSE = 0.031 below the 0.05 acceptance threshold. Velocity field comparison with PIV shows 4.8% spatially averaged relative error. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient evidence to support the COU decision to accept the device design for CPB use.",
